</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_361" id="179v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_361_r1l1"><expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Poſſeken <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒum Rotemperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_361_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd eẅch vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> geleyts für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rat <expan>ʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> begert habt etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l4">Nu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> wir vns / daʒ vor dem <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Crıſtag nıht rat bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l5"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> denn auf nu montag . Jſt eẅch denn ʒu wıllen auf <expan>dıeſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l6">ʒeıt ʒu vns ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . So ſüllt Jr vnd dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> . ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l8">vnd von vns für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ongeuerde 
<add><ab facs="#facs_361_r1l7">ʒwen tag </ab></add> geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l9">wellen wır eẅr rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören . Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_361_r1l11">dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> thome <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_361" id="179v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Posseken, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zum Rotemperg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und ewch und den
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> geleyts für <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        rat <expan>zukome<ex>n</ex></expan> begert habt etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan>
                        wir uns, daz vor <app>
<note><q type="date">dem <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                cristag</q>25.12.1421</note>
</app> niht rat bey uns <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> denn <app>
<note><q type="date">auf nu montag</q>22.12.1421</note>
</app>; ist ewch denn zu willen, auf <expan>dieselbe<ex>n</ex></expan> zeit
                        zu uns zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so süllt ir und die
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geverde <add>zwen tag</add> geleyt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, so wellen wir ewr rede
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn wo wir ewch lieb oder
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Thome
                        <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
